Titolo: Card Hunter

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Card Hunter is a browser-based flash game that combines elements of a digital collectible card game with a table-top board game.
The game is developed by Blue Manchu Games headed by Irrational Games co-founder, Jon Chey. The development team also consists of other former Irrational Games and Looking Glass Studios employees, as well as consultants who previously worked on Magic: The Gathering. It was initially released as a web-browser based game in September 2013, with a standalone client released for Microsoft Windows and OS X in July 2015. On December 22, 2020, Blue Manchu transferred ownership of the game to The Knights of Unity, who are continuing to update and maintain the game.